                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Hello! Thank you for contacting the Family Support Program. How can I help you today?</p>
                    <button onclick="copyToClipboard(this)" class="copy-btn text-sm text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 flex items-center gap-1">
